# General Conventions

- ES6+ only: const/let, arrow functions, template literals — no var
- camelCase for functions/variables, PascalCase for classes, UPPER_SNAKE_CASE for constants
- All constants in src/constants.js — no magic numbers anywhere else
- Max 150 lines per file — split into managers if larger
- No global variables — all state on `this.game`
- All script tags must have type="module"
